name: WALTERINU
description: Walter Inu is a 100% community-driven memecoin based on the famous bull terrier "Walter" meme that went viral in 2018. The community has already established itself as one of the most active on Twitter with a multitude of memes being spread daily. The team is very ambitious with aspirations of creating multiple usecases such as a "Meme Creator", a launchpad referred to as "The Dog House", as well as integrating a full-fledged DAO infrastructure in the future. With ties to Doge & Cheems as being an original dog meme, the community believes they will take the meme market by storm.
